		<img src="includes/newscope.png" alt="Welcome to Dioptrice"><p class="welcome">Dioptrice is an effort to gather information on all surviving refracting telescopes created prior to 1775 held in museums and collections around the world. The database  research tool to study the development of the telescope and its iconographic significance as well as a way for collections to make information regarding their telescopes available to a wider research community.</p>
